<HEADLINE>
<P>
GREYHOUND TALKS BREAK DOWN AMID VIOLENCE CHARGES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
