<HEADLINE>
<P>
PALOMAR WINS SOFTBALL TITLE, 9-1 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Celeste Sanchez pitched a four-hitter to lead Palomar College to a 9-1 victory 
over San Diego Mesa in the championship game of the Golden West softball 
tournament Sunday at Golden West. 
</P>
<P>
Sanchez improves to 5-0 and Palomar, the defending state champion, is 25-3. 
</P>
<P>
Earlier Sunday, Palomar had defeated Golden West, 4-0, in a semifinal game. San 
Diego Mesa defeated Saddleback, 2-1, in the other semifinal. 
</P>
